{"tid":1941101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯陳恒鑌否認發布政府加強防控假消息 引發新一輪搶購潮","createTime":"2020-03-24T08:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T08:05:03.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e26590d0bbdaea31bfc2d3d743a5407994e71937","tid":1941101,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:04:28.000Z","msg":"陳恒鑌否認發布政府加強防控假消息<br />\n<br />\n網上謠傳行政長官林鄭月娥下午舉行記者會，公佈多項嚴厲的抗疫措施，即時通訊軟件亦流傳，相關訊息是由民建聯立法會議員陳恒鑌發放。陳恒鑌回應指自己與事件無關，批評有人不負責任，企圖造成社會恐慌，引發新一輪搶購潮，呼籲市民小心求證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276056&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1276056%26csid%3D261_341&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b785eede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276056&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f787e9b8b21234230bc87683fdfa3b97ebd611dd","tid":1941101,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}